```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "User's Environment"
        Client[Client Application]
    end

    subgraph "Google Cloud Platform"
        CR[Cloud Run: menu-service]
        MSC[Container: Quarkus App]
        VPC[Serverless VPC Connector]
        DB[(Cloud SQL for PostgreSQL)]
    end

    Client -- HTTP Request (e.g., GET /menu) --> CR
    CR -- Routes Request --> MSC
    MSC -- SQL Query --> VPC
    VPC -- Forwards to Private IP --> DB
    DB -- Returns Query Results --> VPC
    VPC -- Forwards Results --> MSC
    MSC -- Formats JSON Response --> CR
    CR -- HTTP Response --> Client
```
